    "title": "Agano la Mungu na Wafalme wa Israeli",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "agano la mungu na wafalme wa israeli",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Solomoni alitambua jukumu lake kama mrithi wa Daudi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:7\">1 Wafalme 3:7</a>). Mfalme mzee Daudi alimshauri Solomoni kufuata sheria zote za Mungu alizopewa Mose ili &quot;afanikiwe katika yote anayofanya na popote anapoelekea&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:3\">2:3</a>). Uaminifu wa Solomoni ungetimiza ahadi za Mungu kwa Daudi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:4\">1 Wafalme 2:4</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:5-2Sam7:16\">2 Samweli 7:5–16</a>). Mapema katika utawala wake, alionyesha kwa makusudi upendo wa Baba yake na uaminifu kwa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:3\">1 Wafalme 3:3</a>). Alitambua kwamba Mungu alikuwa ametimiza ahadi zake kwa Daudi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:23-1Kgs8:26\">8:23–26</a>).</p><p>Mara kadhaa wakati wa utawala wa Solomoni, Mungu alionyesha asili ya kudumu ya agano lake maalum na Daudi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:14\">1 Wafalme 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:4-1Kgs9:5\">9:4–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:38\">11:38</a>). Mungu alimhukumu Solomoni na wafalme wa baadaye kulingana na uaminifu wao kwa agano hilo ikilinganishwa na Daudi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:12-1Kgs11:13\">11:12–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:8\">14:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:3-1Kgs15:5\">15:3–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:11\">11</a>). Idhini na baraka za Mungu au kutoridhika na hukumu zilitokana na kama watu walitii au walikiuka sheria yake (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:1-Deut28:68\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 28</a>).</p><p>Katika enzi za wafalme, Mungu aliwalaani watu wa Israeli kwa makusudi ya kukataa sheria zilizoandikwa za Bwana katika sheria na zile zilizotolewa na manabii wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:13-2Kgs17:17\">2 Wafalme 17:13–17</a>). Kukataa kwao Mungu kulisababisha hukumu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:18-2Kgs17:23\">2 Wafalme 17:18–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:11-2Kgs21:15\">21:11–15</a>).</p><p>Jinsi Mungu alivyoshughulika na wafalme wa Israeli ni mfano kwa wale walio katika agano na Mungu kupitia Yesu. Leo, watu wa Mungu wanapaswa kumpenda Yesu na kufuata amri zake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:21\">Yohana 14:21</a>). Wanapaswa kubaki waaminifu katika mambo yote (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:21\">Mathayo 25:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:10-Luke16:12\">Luka 16:10–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:14\">2 Timotheo 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:7\">4:7</a>). Wale wanaofuata mfano wa Daudi wa uaminifu watapata sifa kutoka kwa Mungu (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:22\">Matendo 13:22</a>). Wale wanaokiri jina la Yesu, mrithi wa Daudi, na kujitolea kwa Mungu na neno lake watajitahidi kuishi maisha safi na yanayompendeza Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:32-Acts13:37\">Matendo 13:32–37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:20-Heb13:21\">Waebrania 13:20–21</a>). Wanajua watapokea zawadi nyingi nzuri kutoka kwa Mungu ambazo zitadumu milele (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:8\">2 Timotheo 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">Ufunuo 2:10</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:19-Gal5:21\">Wagalatia 5:19–21</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:5-2Sam7:17\">2 Samweli 7:5–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:2-1Kgs2:4\">1 Wafalme 2:2–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:3-1Kgs3:15\">3:3–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:22-1Kgs8:26\">8:22–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:1-1Kgs9:9\">9:1–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:1-1Kgs11:13\">11:1–13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:29-1Kgs11:39\">29–39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:7-1Kgs14:16\">14:7–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:1-1Kgs15:5\">15:1–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:11\">11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:13-2Kgs17:23\">2 Wafalme 17:13–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:11-2Kgs21:15\">21:11–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:21-Acts13:23\">Matendo 13:21–23</a></p>",
